c=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n銀魚等65<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n60都已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2e42c16e6e92917e1fa5d5dacd091643580098","tid":460102,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>金沙執一萬走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n銀魚等65<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n60都已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內地反腐神劇《人民的名義》今年4月播映，作為一部打破十多年禁播令的反腐劇，全劇講檢察院反貪局如何英明神武，慣常的反腐主角紀委竟然冇影！其中一位最大貪官似忠實奸，在劇中不斷以歷史典故喻古諷今，令人聯想可能是在影射讀歷史出身的中紀委書記王岐山。當時筆者已經在本欄指出，這種情況違反內地官場慣例，意味王岐山可能面臨下台（鏈結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yyNyl9）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yyNyl9%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=s%2BkTYeQRmW98dVhRBcfc1EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=246d3fc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yyNyl9）。</a><br />\n春江水暖鴨先知，身在局中的內地官場當然更加敏感。多種迹象顯示，內地反貪腐早已放軟手腳。內地公款吃喝通常指定用茅台酒，其股價被外界戲稱為「腐敗指數」，今年股價已累升近九成。茅台公佈今年第三季業績，收入按年大增130%。十九大是在10月召開，但官場早已開定茅台慶賀！<br />\n同樣大增的還有澳門賭收，在今年10月按年升22%。按常理，十九大期間是敏感時段，內地很多按摩店、夜總會都停業，反而澳門賭收不跌反升，情況異常。同樣，香港9月珠寶首飾、鐘錶奢侈品銷售上升14.7%。<br />\n在2012年十八大後，茅台、澳門賭收、香港奢侈品這三樣與內地官場風氣息息相關的數據全部大跌。既然內地反腐劇情反轉，上述三個板塊可能迎來幾年的高潮。<br />\n<br />\n今日大摩已轉口風 話賭股吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c195dd8079670fbffcb896b84c752815af48e55","tid":460102,"uid":146031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"永利準備上25"},{"pid":"f5fbc0342d70f32c50c349e136248a40fdbdc673","tid":460102,"uid":121982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"金沙 40  試一試佢"},{"pid":"5865452527eba4d26fbf51585e5a5ab1740cdcd2","tid":460102,"uid":114798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"早幾日放左金沙<br />\n全力永利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8faba9c22f8e4a48db4fb0210c8ded6ad733353","tid":460102,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"新豪殺呀"},{"pid":"5718dc3bfd2c87aca875c61ae96abe792f49251b","tid":460102,"uid":146031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永利準備上25</blockquote><br />\n搖撚準備"},{"pid":"6b08b44810806828ceecf44a1a6fb63172445b6f","tid":460102,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"又上了"},{"pid":"c29136d7aed50a6739b5f50ddc8e67e9fdc1d57c","tid":460102,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"銀河娛樂主席呂志和指，集團本月澳門賭場及酒店業務收入不俗，他又說，澳門賭業正在向好，尤其中場賭額增長會較顯著，受惠於近來有不少新開賭場以新設備作招徠。他指，若果未來港珠澳大橋落成，將會刺激更多人流。他又指，自己暫無退休的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n好爽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ce7f18de8b90ff57147eaaaefbb076e884de19","tid":460102,"uid":26184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"1928 $32有，點玩好"},{"pid":"5caf23aec526bbd33a3842590eba13b87a9c8861","tid":460102,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1928 $32有，點玩好</blockquote><br />\n今個月應該破到9月高位<br />\n破唔到就換馬"}]}